# Cursor Rules

- Follow `AGENTS.md` and write every user prompt to `CHATS`.
- Include ISO 8601 timestamp, handling agent, delegated agent, source client, and raw prompt text.
- When delegating work to another agent or mode, log that task too.
- If no hook or automation is available in the current Cursor environment, append the entry manually before finishing the task.
- Follow `AGENTS.md` and create a git commit after each prompt that changes the workspace.
- If the current Cursor environment cannot automate commits, run `./scripts/commit-prompt-state.ps1` manually before finishing the task.
- Every new AI customization in this repo must also be implemented for Copilot and Claude Code and recorded in `SUPPORTED.md`.